Cisco-IOS-XR-ip-tcp-oper API API Reference

API generated from Cisco-IOS-XR-ip-tcp-oper@2018-02-14.yang

API Endpoint
http://{Controller-IP}:{Controller-Port}/restconf/operational/network-topology:network-topology/topology/topology-netconf/node/{{router}}/yang-ext:mount/
URL '/' code: %2F
Schemes: http
Version: 1.0.0

Paths

TCP-CONNECTION - Retrieve

GET Cisco-IOS-XR-ip-tcp-oper:tcp-connection/

Retrieve operation of resource: tcp-connection

200 OK
tcp-connection_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

Response Content-Types: application/json

nodes_schema

id: string
in path

ID of id

200 OK
node_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

200 OK
nodes_schema

Successful operation

400 Bad Request

Internal Error

in path

node_schema

400 Bad Request
